data.description: New roof in 2021!!!! Motivated Seller. Great home in a much sought-after neighborhood, offers a captivating blend of charm, functionality, and cool factor. The open-concept layout, flooded with natural light, creates a seamless flow between 2 living spaces!!! The brand new kitchen with modern appliances is a culinary haven, and overlooks the huge den and truly relaxing screened-in, back porch. The master bedroom is a peaceful retreat with plenty of space for your king-size bed, and offers a wonderfully renovated en-suite bathroom. The backyard oasis is great for relaxation and entertaining. Conveniently located 2 blocks from the trendy shops, restaurants, bars, and art galleries of the Magazine St corridor. Assumable VA loan at approximately 2.5% interest rate for qualified Buyer!!! Schedule a showing today and experience the allure of 3714 Laurel Street.
